title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 15 2021

description:
Non-prostate owners have opinions on paternity leave. MLB took the All-Star game from Georgia, now Atlanta will host National League Championship Series. Worst mayor in the country tries to remove Thomas Jefferson statue from NYC City Hall. Plant-based burgers are bad for the environment. DC mayor tries to cancel Chappelle. Idaho doctor: 'We've lost the war, COVID is here to stay.' because of the unvaccinated? FDA panel endorses Moderna ‘half dose’ booster 6 months after 2nd dose.
